title: Cowboy Junkies 2000-02-20 @ The Music Farm - Charleston, SC
description:
After 1994, this is the tour that I have the most affection for, because in February I drove to St. Louis to see the band at Mississippi Nights on Valentine&#039;s Day. They were on fire that night, and driving back through the plains of Kansas I got the idea for trying to make sure all these excellent shows got taped, which has led to this website!

 

This show from the Winter Waltz has some great performances. Margo alludes to being a little tired, and something about Disneyland, but I feel that the music shines regardless.
